latestIgtvVideos.title: Haircare Session With Vogue India | DIY Hairstyle | Coconut oil mask
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I can’t think of a better way to spend a lazy afternoon than this – exchanging notes with like-minded women and discussing all things beauty! And that’s exactly what I did recently when I was invited to an exclusive grooming session by Vogue India. We got expert advice from Vogue India’s beauty editor Sneha Mankani and hair expert, Dr Aparna. The session was so helpful, that I decided to make a video with everything I learned from it.
So this video is focused on hair care and hairstyling – I definitely know you’ll find at least one tip in here that will work for your hair. I have also done a DIY using Nihar Naturals coconut oil, which has made my frizzy hair soft and silky! Do let me know if you like the hairstyle and hair mask.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Keeping Women Safe in Durga Puja
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This Pujo, Maa Durga will be watching over you and keeping you safe! For their new initiative #ThirdEye, @niharnaturals has partnered with some of the major pandals in the city like Badamtala Ashar Sangha, Deshopriyo Park and Singhi Park and have installed 24/7 surveillance security cameras. The cameras are masked as Durga Maa's third eye and will be monitored continuously by the pandal’s security officers. Meet one such officer, Jaba Mondal, who will be Maa Durga’s #thirdeye this Pujo and hear what she has to say about this initiative.
Go visit the pandals and check out the #ThirdEye. If you spot one, click a picture, share it on social media and tag @niharnaturals
#thethirdeyeiswatching
